# Image Intelligence with SparkleIcon User-Driven Node Creation

## Current Architecture (What Exists)

The document intelligence pipeline works as follows:

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Upload["User uploads PDF"] --> Parse["parseDocument(file)"]
    Parse --> InsertCard["Insert AttachmentCardView (status: uploading)"]
    InsertCard --> ProcessUpload["processDocumentForNode()"]
    ProcessUpload --> StatusReady["Update status: ready"]
    StatusReady --> OnDocReady["onDocumentReady callback"]
    OnDocReady --> AnalyzeSpawn["analyzeAndSpawn()"]
    AnalyzeSpawn --> GeminiCall["analyzeDocument() via Gemini"]
    GeminiCall --> CacheResult["cacheExtraction() on AttachmentMeta"]
    CacheResult --> BuildSpawn["buildInsightSpawn()"]
    BuildSpawn --> AutoCreate["AUTO-CREATE child node + edge"]
```



Key files:

- `[useDocumentAgent.ts](src/features/documentAgent/hooks/useDocumentAgent.ts)` (115 lines) -- orchestrates analysis AND auto-spawns child node
- `[useIdeaCardImageHandlers.ts](src/features/canvas/hooks/useIdeaCardImageHandlers.ts)` (106 lines) -- wires `onDocumentReady` callback
- `[AttachmentCardView.tsx](src/features/canvas/components/nodes/AttachmentCardView.tsx)` (110 lines) -- TipTap NodeView for attachments
- `[imageDescriptionService.ts](src/features/knowledgeBank/services/imageDescriptionService.ts)` (69 lines) -- Gemini Vision for images (hardcoded `'image/jpeg'` MIME type bug)
- `[WorkspaceControls.tsx](src/features/workspace/components/WorkspaceControls.tsx)` (76 lines) -- top canvas toolbar

## Target Architecture

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Upload["User uploads PDF or Image"] --> Parse["parseDocument() or describeImageWithAI()"]
    Parse --> InsertCard["Insert AttachmentCardView (status: uploading)"]
    InsertCard --> StatusReady["Update status: ready"]
    StatusReady --> AutoAnalyze{"autoAnalyzeAttachments ON?"}
    AutoAnalyze -->|Yes| SubCheck{"Premium user?"}
    SubCheck -->|Yes| AnalyzeSilent["analyzeOnly() -- Gemini, cache result"]
    SubCheck -->|No| NoOp["Skip analysis"]
    AutoAnalyze -->|No| NoOp
    AnalyzeSilent --> ShowSparkle["Show SparkleIcon on AttachmentCardView"]
    ShowSparkle --> UserTap["User taps SparkleIcon"]
    UserTap --> SpawnNode["spawnInsightNode() -- create child node + edge"]

    NoOp --> ManualAnalyze["User taps /analyze slash command"]
    ManualAnalyze --> AnalyzeSilent
```



Key changes:

1. **Decouple** `analyzeAndSpawn` into `analyzeOnly` (background LLM + cache) and `spawnInsightNode` (create child)
2. **Image support:** Route image uploads through `describeImageWithAI` to produce `parsedText`, then into `analyzeOnly`
3. **SparkleIcon on AttachmentCardView:** Appears when `extraction` is cached but child node not yet spawned; user taps to create
4. **Toolbar toggle:** Mirror the settings `autoAnalyzeAttachments` toggle in `WorkspaceControls`
5. **Label rename:** "documents" to "attachments" everywhere

